comments.body:
> I think the tests should've gone in `test/system/505-networking-pasta.bats`

@ricardobranco777 I think in a near future we'll need to add more comprehensive tests checking edge cases and specific functionalities of forwarding to custom network using pasta, see also https://github.com/containers/container-libs/pull/755#issuecomment-4395861122 for context, and those would belong in `505-networking-pasta.bats`.

But for the moment the test, rather simple, needs to run against rootlessport as well as pasta, so that's not really a specific pasta test and I feel like `500-networking.bats` is a better match. What do you think?
